Participation
Class Participation

java.lang.Object
  Participation.Participation
All Implemented Interfaces:
java.io.Serializable
public class Participation
extends java.lang.Object
implements java.io.Serializable

An instance of this class represents a unit of participation to a certain service. A customer can buy participations. See also the background provided in ApplicationLogic.
